{
  "3170560": {
    "name": "天际防线:空岛传说",
    "steam_appid": 3170560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在遥远的神话时代，天空中漂浮着无数的空岛，它们是由古老的魔法和元素力量维系的奇迹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你将成为重生的南瓜人王子，修建防御，布下陷阱抵御外敌。建设家园，重振经济，让王国重见辉煌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras/41bac7f58378a5df1379b1bd85d0c6db.avif?t=1758090871\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras_big/41bac7f58378a5df1379b1bd85d0c6db.avif?t=1758090871 width=800 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-百废待兴-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整座王城几乎被历史洪流化为废墟，把废墟和荒地铲平，让它们变为人们的住房和耕地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras/23d82e092d05e0ee21f6de9522ce1e27.avif?t=1758090871\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras_big/23d82e092d05e0ee21f6de9522ce1e27.avif?t=1758090871 width=800 height=263 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>城市建造不可不尝，建造并发展城市的民生建筑，会让你的城市更加繁荣美丽！试着从王国悲戚的废墟起步，建设起一座繁华都市。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras/ea630aaf8396710657aa7f84012acdeb.avif?t=1758090871\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras/1d0cc20a1be73c7ddad8de747e5f114e.avif?t=1758090871\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras/f43be775a851328000af518c8f50698b.avif?t=1758090871\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-建设防御-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >箭塔？雷电塔？法师塔？陷阱？只要好用，统统给我建起来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过，如果要打赢这些怪物，我们或许需要“小小的经济支持”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras/501652cd8797c3d96470875f4a5fca65.avif?t=1758090871\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras_big/501652cd8797c3d96470875f4a5fca65.avif?t=1758090871 width=800 height=263 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我们有整整8种防御塔，并且拥有许多【变种建筑】，你可以借助魔法道具的力量改造这些本来平平无奇的防御</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras/ae832b0c4821dc9208b016362d217f68.avif?t=1758090871\" width=654 height=544 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras/3141f83f9c43ed5338a45510945913e7.avif?t=1758090871\" width=426 height=598 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-抵抗外敌-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王国曾经辉煌，却在风霜中褪色。但那些野心勃勃的敌人们不会就此善罢甘休，无论是魔物还是空中强盗，我们都不能让他们靠近岛之心！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>已有多达百种怪物，他们拥有极其各自的特性。当我们在不同的地区冒险时，需要想办法对抗不同的敌人。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras/33b7aee2d215047a4da23b6de4a0487e.avif?t=1758090871\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras_big/33b7aee2d215047a4da23b6de4a0487e.avif?t=1758090871 width=800 height=263 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-魔力世界-</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你仍记得生前曾使用过的那些魔法吗？或许没什么印象，但没关系，驾驶着王国空岛不断的冒险，找回那些失去的东西！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras/216ab52aba5c1542f59d3c2fb3945c3a.avif?t=1758090871\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170560/extras_big/216ab52aba5c1542f59d3c2fb3945c3a.avif?t=1758090871 width=800 height=262 /></span>蓄积魔力，才能使用强大的法术，这是世界的常识！</p>",
